              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Gaseous 15N(2) (99.4% isotopic purity) is introduced",
                "into the 2 mm annular cell through a needle valve, and",
                "condensed using the ILL's orange heliumexchange",
                "cryostat. The sample temperature is then lowered to",
                "the solid alpha-phase - nitrogen at temperatures",
                "of 5.9, 11, 15, 20, 25 K ."
              ]
            }
          ],
